headline.print_headline: Boehner Lauds Doctor Who Saved Lawmaker's Baby
headline.main: Boehner Lauds Doctor Who Saved Lawmaker's Baby

lead_paragraph: In a break from his chamber's often acrid political divisions, a choked-up House Speaker John Boehner prompted two bipartisan standing ovations on Wednesday when he praised the doctor who helped a congresswoman's infant survive a rare fetal condition.
